HEADWORD: Opinicus
<hw>O*pin"i*cus</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Her.)</fld>
<def>An imaginary animal borne as a charge, having wings, an eagle's
head, and a short tail; -- sometimes represented without
wings.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

